NPCName "QuarterMaster Pachini"
Location "Vault 31, First floor supply room"
Description "Pachini is the female vault dweller model standing in the room full of crates, to the east."
Unknown_Desc "This woman has a stern look on her face."
Known_Desc "Quartermaster Pachini looks pissed, as usual."
Detailed_Desc "This woman holds herself with an air of confidence that implies she is used to being in charge. She looks at you with a hint of disdain."
Node "Start"
notes ""
{
NPCText "<PC>, how many times do I have to tell you? I can't give you anything unless you've got the right forms."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Pretty please? All I need is a Hydroelectric Magnetosphere Regulator..." linkto "A"  notes ""
          int=6 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "(Frantically search your pockets) I could've sworn it was right here..." linkto "B" conditions { CHECK_SKILL speech > 29 } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've got them right here." linkto "X"  notes "This option should appear after the PC gets the Mr. Handy OS quest from Ken Neff."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Geez, do you always get wake up on the wrong side of the bed?" linkto "D"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You pretty." linkto "C"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I got form! I got form!" linkto "X"  notes "This option should appear after the PC gets the Mr. Handy OS quest from Ken Neff."
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Uh oh. I forget. I come back with forms. Bye Bye!" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "What the hell are you talking about?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wait. You mean you don't know what it is either?" linkto "G"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "B"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Hah! I can't believe this! You finally had the form, and you lost it?"
      options {
          int=6 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Ohgodohgodohgodohgod, Duane is going to kick my ass!" linkto "E" conditions { CHECK_SKILL speech > 34 } notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Shit! Please, you gotta help me out!" linkto "F"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "C"
notes ""
{
NPCText "(She smirks) That's very sweet of you, <PC>. Now do you have a form or not?"
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Uh Uh. But you still pretty. Like flower." linkto "K"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "X"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Wha? (Her eyes widen) You've even filled them out in triplicate!"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Bet you thought this day would never come, huh?" linkto "J"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I got forms good, huh?" linkto "J"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "D"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Look, its nothing personal, okay? I just need the forms. Come back when you have them."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "(End)" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "E"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Duane sent you?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yeah. He wanted me to pick up an electronics manual and some mentats." linkto "H"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "F"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Why the hell would I do that?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Aw, c'mon Pachino. I had it two seconds ago, I did!" linkto "D"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "G"
notes ""
{
NPCText "(She rolls her eyes) You moron. Come back when you've got the forms."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "(End)" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "H"
notes "Exp reward(?) for convincing her to give you the manua and mentats."
{
NPCText "Tell you what.I'll let you go this time, but when you see him, ask him where the fuck he was last night. I waited two hours for that asshole and he never even showed up!"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Whoa! Take it easy. I'm sure he had a good reason." linkto "I"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "I"
notes ""
{
NPCText "He better have the best reason in the whole goddamn universe! I swear, if he tries ANY more bullshit, I'm gonna castrate him with my bare hands..."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "(End)" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "J"
notes "When we decide what the player gets to start off with, this is when it is received."
{
NPCText "Okay, well lets see here. I'm supposed to give you... (She hands over some supplies, a weapon, and armor). That should be all of it."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks, Pachino. See you later." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yay! (Give her a big hug)" linkto "L"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "K"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Cool it, Romeo. Come back when you have the forms, okay?"
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "(End)" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "L"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Wha...? I... guess I'll take that as a thank you."
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Bye Bye!" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
